message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you for $130. I believe it will be very valuable to you.
I'm interested in the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $90.
I understand your position, Bob, but $90 is a bit too low for me. Would you be willing to meet in the middle at $110?
I'm still interested in the product, but I can only go up to $100.
